paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.DoubleType
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.VectorAssembler
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.MinMaxScaler

val extractFeatures = new VectorAssembler()
    .setInputCols(Array("sqft_living"))
    .setOutputCol("features")

val data_extractFeatures = extractFeatures.transform(data)

val scaler = new MinMaxScaler()
  .setInputCol("features")
  .setOutputCol("scaled_features")

val data_scaler = scaler.fit(data_extractFeatures).transform(data_extractFeatures)

data_scaler.printSchema()
data_scaler.registerTempTable("data")

##Calcul d'un model de regression lineaire simple + calcul du "root mean squared error (RMSE)"

result.msg: Calcul d'un model de regression lineaire simple + calcul du “root mean squared error (RMSE)”

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.mllib.evaluation.RegressionMetrics
import org.apache.spark.ml.regression.LinearRegression

val lr = new LinearRegression()
    .setMaxIter(10)
    .setFeaturesCol("scaled_features")
    .setLabelCol("label")
    
val pipeline = new Pipeline().setStages(Array(extractFeatures, scaler, lr))

val model = pipeline.fit(training)

val prediction = model.transform(test).select("id", "label", "prediction")
prediction.registerTempTable("prediction")

val prediction_rdd = prediction.rdd.map(p => (p.getAs[Double]("label"), p.getAs[Double]("prediction")))
val metrics = new RegressionMetrics(prediction_rdd)

println(s"MSE = ${metrics.meanSquaredError}")
println(s"RMSE = ${metrics.rootMeanSquaredError}")
println(s"R-squared = ${metrics.r2}")
println(s"MAE = ${metrics.meanAbsoluteError}")
println(s"Explained variance = ${metrics.explainedVariance}")

##Calcul d'un model de regression lineaire + calcul du "root mean squared error (RMSE)"

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.mllib.evaluation.RegressionMetrics

val max_bedrooms = training.agg(max(training.col("bedrooms"))).head.getInt(0).toDouble;
val max_bathrooms = training.agg(max(training.col("bathrooms"))).head.getDouble(0).toDouble;
val max_sqft_living = training.agg(max(training.col("sqft_living"))).head.getInt(0).toDouble;
val max_sqft_lot = training.agg(max(training.col("sqft_lot"))).head.getInt(0).toDouble;
val max_floors = training.agg(max(training.col("floors"))).head.getDouble(0).toDouble;
val max_zipcode = training.agg(max(training.col("zipcode"))).head.getInt(0).toDouble;

val trainingData = training.map(sale => LabeledPoint(sale.getAs[Integer]("price").toDouble, Vectors.dense(
    sale.getAs[Integer]("bedrooms").toDouble / max_bedrooms,
    sale.getAs[Double]("bathrooms").toDouble / max_bathrooms,
    sale.getAs[Integer]("sqft_living").toDouble / max_sqft_living,
    sale.getAs[Integer]("sqft_lot").toDouble / max_sqft_lot,
    sale.getAs[Double]("floors").toDouble / max_floors,
    sale.getAs[Integer]("zipcode").toDouble / max_zipcode
    )))

val numIterations = 10
val model = LinearRegressionWithSGD.train(trainingData, numIterations)

model.weights

val testData = test.map(sale => LabeledPoint(sale.getAs[Integer]("price").toDouble, Vectors.dense(
    sale.getAs[Integer]("bedrooms").toDouble / max_bedrooms,
    sale.getAs[Double]("bathrooms").toDouble / max_bathrooms,
    sale.getAs[Integer]("sqft_living").toDouble / max_sqft_living,
    sale.getAs[Integer]("sqft_lot").toDouble / max_sqft_lot,
    sale.getAs[Double]("floors").toDouble / max_floors,
    sale.getAs[Integer]("zipcode").toDouble / max_zipcode
    )))

val valuesAndPreds = testData.map { point =>
  val prediction = model.predict(point.features)
  (point.label, prediction)
}

testData.take(10)
trainingData.take(10)
valuesAndPreds.take(10)

val metrics = new RegressionMetrics(valuesAndPreds)
println(s"MSE = ${metrics.meanSquaredError}")
println(s"RMSE = ${metrics.rootMeanSquaredError}")
println(s"R-squared = ${metrics.r2}")
println(s"MAE = ${metrics.meanAbsoluteError}")
println(s"Explained variance = ${metrics.explainedVariance}")
